hopobject.body: Get a job wahl grooming kit india A separate survey also released on Monday shed new light onthe youngest generation of millionaires. The FidelityMillionaire Outlook shows that rich Gen X and Gen Yers areearning more money and amassing more assets than baby boomermillionaires. Salaries average $677,000 for those 48 and youngercompared to $198,000 for those older, and total average assetsare $5.7 versus $5.2 million.
